in our part of the world,

00:05:40.239 --> 00:05:41.805
postcolonial Southeast Asia,

00:05:41.829 --> 00:05:44.278
in so many ways, for me,

00:05:45.364 --> 00:05:51.628
bears residual traces to ideas, tropes,

